Interface AttributesSummary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItemFeatureEntry
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface AttributesSummary
extends ItemFeatureEntry
    A representation of the model object 'Attributes Summary'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Attributes
    • Output Prefix
